{"tid":1817002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲少年涉元朗掟汽油彈被捕","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T17:46:26.000Z","uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"abea3ce024a294bd8f478bab4e22bcdbdf2b60a4","tid":1817002,"uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"一名15歲少年涉嫌於元朗投擲懷疑汽油彈被捕，事件中無人受傷。  警方今晨（1月8日）1時許接案，指有少年在元朗鳯翔路100號朗晴居對開，投擲懷疑汽油彈。警員發現馬路有兩處燻黑，並在鳯琴街對開截停一名少年，在他身上檢獲兩個打火機、一批手套、五條毛巾及一把剪刀。  少年涉嫌縱火、藏有工具可作非法用途及未能出示身分證明文件被捕，現正被扣查。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5209a946d35091e5df28e7885b374cc3410b7a68","tid":1817002,"uid":198590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:49:34.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#153956 - 千萬窮能</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>係時候諗定輸左後點做 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔係講笑各位連青人, 係時候諗定, 日日9叫唱歌既革命輸得7788, 準備比人上門清算<br />\n<br />\n1,2,3,4定10年, 寫定張平安紙交帶</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>睇你地班人既所謂革命 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎黎去去係街9 叫<br />\n<br />\n見警就縮<br />\n<br />\n咁攪法攪到幾時先成功？留比你地個孫接手曱命？<br />\n<br />\n初初都好笑消閒下時間，可惜越睇越悶</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1685603/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1685603/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>又話朦面法無用 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>太子站外人呢？平時好多架. <img